{"calories":"830","carbs":null,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"This life-changing (no, but seriously) pasta dish was such a smash hit that we just \u003ci\u003ehad\u003c/i\u003e to bring it back...and fast. Fresh, tender spaghetti is coated in a comforting tomato and basil sauce, which gets extra depth from white wine and crushed red pepper. Finished with salty Parmesan and a generous portion of ethereally creamy burrata cheese, this is a must.eat.right.now sort of situation. ","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"d66b3f61d3","fat":null,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17911/1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0137.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17911/menu_small_1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0137.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17910/1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0148_2.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17907/1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0129_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17907/hero_1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0129_1.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17907/menu_small_1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0129_1.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17907/small_square_1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0129_1.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17907/medium_square_1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0129_1.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/17907/recipe_profile_page_1986_Fresh_Spaghetti_with_Cherry_Tomato_Sauce_and_Burrata___0129_1.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Fresh Spaghetti with Cherry Tomato Sauce and Burrata","novice_time":"","portion_count":2,"prep_time":"25-35","pro_time":"","product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":null,"public_slug":"fresh-spaghetti-with-cherry-tomato-sauce-and-burrata","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/10242/recipe_card20170116-4-13gio6j.pdf","recipe_id":1986,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Fresh Spaghetti with Burrata","subtitle":"with Cherry Tomato Sauce and Burrata","title":"Fresh Spaghetti","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did! \u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eCovering the water will help it boil faster and prevent it from evaporating. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eStarchy pasta cooking water will give your sauce a perfect consistency and help it to cling to the noodles. Keep adding it until the sauce is silky—you may need more than you think. \u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBurrata is delicate, so be sure to handle it gently. Discard only the watery liquid from the container, not cheese solids.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["10\" large pot with lid","10\" medium high-sided pan"],"id":1986,"ingredients":["garlic","yellow onion","fresh basil","crushed red pepper","white wine","14-ounce can cherry tomatoes","tomato purée","sugar","fresh spaghetti","grated Parmesan cheese","burrata cheese"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"yellow onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/27/medium_square_yellow-onion-test.jpg"},{"name":"fresh basil","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1274/medium_square_medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"crushed red pepper","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/39/medium_square_CRUSHED_RED_PEPPER_copy.jpg"},{"name":"white wine","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/256/medium_square_WHITE_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"14-ounce can cherry tomatoes","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1519/medium_square_tomatoes.jpg"},{"name":"tomato purée","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1095/medium_square_medium_square_ingredients-9.jpg"},{"name":"sugar","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"teaspoon","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/292/medium_square_sugar-test.jpg"},{"name":"fresh spaghetti","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/875/medium_square_fresh_spaghetti.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/22/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"burrata cheese","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1087/medium_square_medium_square_fresh_mozzarella.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16165/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients_1.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eBring a large pot of water to a boil over high heat and cover (see Recipe Tip). Mince \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e, halve, and thinly slice. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e and set aside 1 whole sprig for tomato sauce; roughly chop \u003cstrong\u003eremaining\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eleaves\u003c/strong\u003e, discarding stems.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Sauté Aromatics","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16164/recipe_card_size_2._Saute_Aromatics.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e in a medium high-sided pan over medium heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until soft and translucent, 5-7 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003ecrushed red pepper \u003c/strong\u003e(skip if you want less heat) and \u003cstrong\u003egarlic \u003c/strong\u003eand cook until fragrant, 1 minute more.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Simmer Tomato Sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16163/recipe_card_size_3._Simmer.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003ewhite\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003ewine\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003echerry\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes and their juices\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e tomato purée\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e sugar\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ewhole basil sprig \u003c/strong\u003eto pan with onions. Increase heat to high and bring to a boil, then reduce heat to medium and simmer, breaking up tomatoes, until softened, 5-7 minutes. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eblack\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Remove from heat.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook Spaghetti","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16167/recipe_card_size_4._Cook_Spaghetti.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eSeason boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003espaghetti\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 3 minutes. Reserve \u003cstrong\u003e.5 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, then drain.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Season Spaghetti","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16166/recipe_card_size_5._Season_Spaghetti.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eRemove and discard \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003esprig\u003c/strong\u003e from tomato sauce (it infuses flavor, but doesn't hold up well to heat), then add \u003cstrong\u003espaghetti\u003c/strong\u003e to pan over medium heat. Cook, stirring, until pasta is coated and warmed through, 1-2 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003ereserved pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, 1 tablespoon at a time, until sauce is thick and clings to noodles (see Recipe Tip). Remove from heat and stir in \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e. Taste and add more \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eblack pepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate Spaghetti ","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/16168/recipe_card_size_6._Plate_Spaghetti.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDivide \u003cstrong\u003espaghetti\u003c/strong\u003e evenly between serving plates. Remove \u003cstrong\u003eburrata\u003c/strong\u003e from container, discarding excess liquid (see Recipe Tip). Tear into bite-size pieces and place over spaghetti. Garnish with \u003cstrong\u003echopped basil\u003c/strong\u003e, grab a fork, and twirl away.\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"allergens":[{"name":"Egg","slug":"egg","hex_color":""},{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"feature":[]}}